08:05.320 --> 08:09.080
that can finally clear up the need for all these defences.

08:09.560 --> 08:13.320
Right. So it just clears up anxiety, clears up depressive symptomology.

08:13.320 --> 08:18.000
It can clear up chronic pain and opens a person up to

08:18.960 --> 08:22.680
